Joy Westmore https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joy_Westmore 0 Joy Westmore (née Grissold) (born in 1932, in Australia) is an Australian actress, best known to international television viewers for her long-running role in Prisoner - as friendly but highly ineffectual bespectacled officer Joyce Barry Pringle - in which she won a Penguin Award.
